{"type":null,"faqId":25345,"title":"How do I adjust the photo size?","answer":"<html>\n<head>\n<META http-equiv=\"Content-Type\" content=\"text/html; charset=UTF-8\">\n<style type=\"text/css\">.b1{white-space-collapsing:preserve;}\n.d1{margin: 1.18125in 0.7875in 1.18125in 0.7875in;}\n.p1{margin-left:1.18125in;margin-top:0.11111111in;margin-bottom:0.11111111in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Times New Roman;font-size:10pt;}\n.s1{font-weight:bold;}\n</style>\n</head>\n<body class=\"b1\">\n<div  >\n<p  >\n<span>The photo size depends on the camera resolution. The higher the resolution, the larger the photo.</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<a name=\"ZH-CN_TOPIC_0005891058\"></a><span>For EMUI 2.0 and EMUI 2.3, enter the camera viewfinder mode and select </span><img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=87054\" style=\"width:0.30555555in;height:0.22361112in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/><span>. Select the </span><span class=\"s1\">Camera</span><span> tab and then select </span><span class=\"s1\">Resolution</span><span> to adjust the camera resolution.</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span>For EMUI 3.0, enter the camera viewfinder mode and select </span><img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=87055\" style=\"width:0.20763889in;height:0.14513889in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/><span>. Then select </span><span class=\"s1\">Settings &gt; Resolution</span><span> to adjust the camera resolution.</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span>The size of a photo can also be changed by opening the photo using </span><span class=\"s1\">Gallery</span><span> or another third-party app and cropping the image.</span>\n</p>\n</div>\n</body>\n</html>\n","faqTypeId":null,"faqType":null,"useful":0,"unUseful":0,"languageId":1,"languageName":"en","faqCode":"9425","faqTypeCode":null,"isTop":"0","moduleCode":"faq","productId":null,"productCode":null,"postDate":1430808372000,"seriesProductName":"G6-L11,G760-L01,Jazz-L11,S10-231L,S10-231u,S7-721u,Sophia-L10,Y220-U10,Y221-U22,Y330-U01,Y330-U11,Y330-U11,Y511-U10,Y520-U22,Y550-L01","visitedTimes":2,"isUsefulFlag":null,"score":0,"times":0,"imageList":null,"displayType":"text","justView":"0","fileName":null,"filePath":null,"imagePath":null,"imageName":null,"productIdList":null,"curPage":null,"pageSize":null,"siteCode":null,"statusFlag":"Publish","returnCode":0,"totalRows":null,"keywords":"change, photo, dimensions","avgScore":0.0,"createDate":null,"totalPages":null}